

@startuml
left to right direction
title BITCONSOLE - Core Flow (with CPU Monitor)

actor User

User --> [ButtonTask]

[ButtonTask] --> [Queue] : send event
[Menu/Snake Task] --> [Queue] : receive event

' ==== Display Flow (Apps) ====
[Menu/Snake Task] --> [I2C Mutex] : take
[Menu/Snake Task] --> [Display] : update screen
[Display] --> [Menu/Snake Task] : notify done
[Menu/Snake Task] --> [I2C Mutex] : give

' ==== CPU Monitor ====
[CPU Monitor Task] --> [I2C Mutex] : take
[CPU Monitor Task] --> [Display] : update CPU usage
[Display] --> [CPU Monitor Task] : notify done
[CPU Monitor Task] --> [I2C Mutex] : give
@enduml